3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with automated detection of emotions from facial expressions. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing facial expressions in images. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the potential applications of smile detection in interactive controlling.
